{{page-title "Local"}}

<section>
  This implementation uses a local changeset for the query data stored in the model service.
  <ul>
      <li>The model holds the real data.</li>
      <li>The model has the methods to validate the data going into it.</li>
      <li>The model can only be accessed by the route's controller and anything it passes the changeset to.</li>
  </ul> 

    <QueryParmTester
      @queryText={{this.text}} 
      @formText={{this.formContents.formText}}
      @modelValue={{this.changeset.value}}
      @errorText={{this.modelService.errorText}}
    >
      <:query>
        <LoadPageLink @page="local" @value={{this.queryValue}}/>
        <TextInput @id="queryval" @labelText = " with: " @value={{this.text}} @changed={{this.changeQueryParameter}}/>
      </:query>
      <:input>
        <FormInput @contents={{this.formContents}} @submitted={{this.formSubmitted}}/>
      </:input>
    </QueryParmTester>

</section>


